<event name="START_GAME">
	<text>You are a proud rebel from the Galactic Rebellion, that is planing to take over a Federation sector in the other side of the galaxy. You were given a secret mission to gather data about their fleet which you managed to do successfully. Now you must escape from the Federation to return vital information about their flagship.</text>
</event>

<textList name="GAMEOVER">
	<text>The information will never reach the Rebellion as your ship breaks apart.</text>
</textList>

<event name="TUTORIAL_START">
