<event name="START_BEACON">
	<text>Welcome to a new sector! Get to the exit beacon and jump to the next sector before the pursuing federation ships catch you!</text>
</event>

<event name="START_BEACON_CIVILIAN">
	<text load="START_BEACON_CIVILIAN"/>
</event>
<textList name="START_BEACON_CIVILIAN">
	<text>Although this sector is home to many civilians, the Federation is also constantly on guard here.</text>
	<text>The Federatives patrol this sector, trying to keep out the Rebels. Fortunately, most of their ships have left to defend their base.</text>
	<text>This sector used to be heavely guarded by the Federation, but now there are only a handful of them left here thanks to the Rebellion.</text>
	<text>Some civilian sectors are already under Rebel control, this one is still desperately being protected by the Federation</text>
	<text>You will have to be cautious in this sector. The Federatives have their outposts here and are no doubt looking for you.</text>
</textList>

<event name="START_BEACON_FEDERATION">
	<text load="START_BEACON_FEDERATION"/>
</event>
<textList name="START_BEACON_FEDERATION">
	<text>You need to be careful here, this is an Federation sector.</text>

</textList>


